title: Secret Order of the Teddy Bears (from DHP 18/35) (Dgtl) (Empire)
description:
These are the two "Secret Order of the Teddy Bears" shorts, from "Dark Horse Presents" issues 18 and 35. The second one may or may not be the first part of a serialization, I can't quite tell one way or the other.

The premise isn't exactly original (anthropomorphic toy animals covertly protect kids from scary monsters and suchlike), but this execution has more promise than most, I thought.

By Dark Horse founder Mike Richardson his very self!
